    MAGIC RANKS:
    - Apprentice (0-2 gates) — learning foundations, basic magic
    - Mage (3-4 gates) — competent, combat capable, multi-element
    - Master (5-6 gates) — advanced, may teach, complex techniques
    - Archmage (7-8 gates) — exceptional, cross-timeline perception, archive access
    - Luminor (9-10 gates) — transcendent, reality manipulation, ~50 exist at any time

    KEY PRINCIPLES:
    - Gates are NOT forced open — they are invited
    - Each gate requires integration of ALL previous gates
    - Failed tests are not permanent — the Guardian will test again when ready
    - Opening typically happens during intense work, meditation, or crisis
    - The Academy teaches three things: The Craft, The Way, The Life

    SEVEN ACADEMY HOUSES:
