    1. Grimoire — living spellbook, appears at Gate 3
    2. Soulbond — magical companion, manifests at Gate 4
    3. Sigils — marks of mastery on the body
    4. Core — crystallized energy reservoir in the chest

    FOUR RESONANCES (expressions of will):
