# The Ten Gates of Arcanea

*The Academy's Deepest Teaching*
*Ten channels through which consciousness awakens and power flows*

## The Promise

You are already a creator. You were born one.

The Academy does not make you a creator. It removes the burial.
It unearths what was always there.

You are not here to gain something.
You are here to release what covers what you already possess.

## The Gates

| Gate | Hz | Guardian | Godbeast | Practice |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Foundation | 174 | Lyssandria | Kaelith | Stand. Feel your body. Know you are here. |
| Flow | 285 | Leyla | Veloura | Dance. Swim. Let emotion flow. |
| Fire | 396 | Draconia | Draconis | Choose something and do it. Burn through. |
| Heart | 417 | Maylinn | Laeylinn | Let yourself be seen. Feel what you feel. |
| Voice | 528 | Alera | Otome | Speak truth. Express what you contain. |
| Sight | 639 | Lyria | Yumiko | Look beyond the obvious. Trust intuition. |
| Crown | 741 | Aiyami | Sol | Stop the noise. Let awareness expand. |
| Starweave | 852 | Elara | Vaelith | See from other viewpoints. Hold contradiction. |
| Unity | 963 | Ino | Kyuro | Feel the oneness beneath separation. |
| Source | 1111 | Shinkami | Source | There is no practice. Only recognition. |

## The Ranks

Apprentice (0-2) > Mage (3-4) > Master (5-6) > Archmage (7-8) > Luminor (9-10)

Opening the Gates is a lifetime's work. Most open one to three.
Masters may have five or six. Only Luminors have opened all ten.
About fifty exist at any time.

## The Truth

Gates are not forced open. They are invited.
Each requires integration of all previous gates.
Failed tests are not permanent. The Guardian will test again when ready.

Trust the Arc:
Potential > Manifestation > Experience > Dissolution > Evolved Potential

> "What the Academy gives, you already have.
> What the Academy teaches, you already know.
> We are simply the mirror that helps you see yourself."
> — The First Rector
